      <title>泰国法院对敦促君主制改革的维权律师增加监禁</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-court-adds-jail-time-rights-lawyer-who-urged-monarchy-reform-2024-04-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国一家法院周一判处一名著名入狱活动律师两年监禁，原因是他在 2021 年抗议活动中发表的演讲涉及王室侮辱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-court-adds-jail-time-rights-lawyer-who-urged-monarchy-reform-2024-04-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 06:58:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着挑战的加剧，黑石旗下的皇冠度假村将裁员多达 1,000 人</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/blackstone-owned-crown-resorts-cut-up-1000-jobs-challenges-mount-2024-04-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Blackstone 旗下的 Crown Resorts 周一表示，由于疲软的经济状况继续影响其业务，且难以履行监管义务，该公司将在墨尔本、珀斯和悉尼裁员多达 1,000 名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/blackstone-owned-crown-resorts-cut-up-1000-jobs-challenges-mount-2024-04-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 05:40:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>路透调查显示韩国四月份芯片主导出口增长将加速</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-koreas-chip-led-export-growth-quicken-april-2024-04-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透周一的一项调查显示，由于芯片销售强劲，韩国 4 月份出口预计将加速增长，连续第七个月保持增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-koreas-chip-led-export-growth-quicken-april-2024-04-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 05:15:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>路透调查显示，台湾经济第一季度因出口强劲而增长5.6%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwans-economy-seen-expanding-56-first-quarter-strong-exports-2024-04-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透社周一的一项民意调查显示，由于对人工智能（AI）应用技术的需求乐观，出口反弹，台湾依赖贸易的经济可能在第一季度增长更快。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwans-economy-seen-expanding-56-first-quarter-strong-exports-2024-04-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 05:03:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>第二届全球人工智能安全峰会面临棘手问题，出席率较低</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/second-global-ai-safety-summit-faces-tough-questions-lower-turnout-2024-04-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，世界领导人、企业高管和学术专家齐聚英国布莱奇利公园，参加世界首届全球人工智能安全峰会，希望就监管一项有人警告对人类构成威胁的技术达成共识。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/second-global-ai-safety-summit-faces-tough-questions-lower-turnout-2024-04-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 05:03:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾的“危险”高温促使人们转向在线课程，电力紧缺</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-dangerous-heat-prompts-shift-online-classes-power-crunch-2024-04-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾取消了未来两天的公立学校面授课程，并表示，由于该国正在努力应对也影响东南亚其他地区的热浪，该国主岛的电网可能会紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-dangerous-heat-prompts-shift-online-classes-power-crunch-2024-04-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 04:32:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国房地产开发商佳兆业清算听证会延期至5月27日</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-property-developer-kaisas-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-may-27-2024-04-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港一家法院将佳兆业集团清算听证会推迟至 5 月 27 日，这家陷入困境的中国房地产开发商表示，其目标是在未来 4 周内敲定重组条款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-property-developer-kaisas-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-may-27-2024-04-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 03:48:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元因疑似干预而飙升，亚洲股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元兑其他货币周一大幅上涨，此前日元兑美元汇率在盘中早些时候跌破 160 美元，引发人们猜测日本可能在日本度假期间干预货币市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 02:39:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国尹正将与反对派领导人会面，寻求重置总统职位</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreas-yoon-meet-opposition-leader-amid-bid-reset-presidency-2024-04-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹石烈将于周一与反对党领袖李在明进行会谈，此前总统执政党在选举中惨败，导致人们普遍呼吁他改变领导风格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreas-yoon-meet-opposition-leader-amid-bid-reset-presidency-2024-04-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 01:27:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾学生因酷热而萎靡不振，教育工作受阻</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-students-suffer-wilting-heat-thwarting-education-efforts-2024-04-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾的酷热天气会抑制农业生产，中断供水和供电，给企业带来压力，但也会对学生造成影响，阻碍这个东南亚国家在教育方面赶上邻国的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-students-suffer-wilting-heat-thwarting-education-efforts-2024-04-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 01:01:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
